---
title: Beef Stir-Fry Bowls with Snap Peas and Jasmine Rice
description: This family favourite take-out fake-out will be ready at the dinner table in no time! A sweet and savoury sauce glazes each bite of hearty beef.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-saute-de-boeuf-1ddca6a8.jpg
